<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！咔嚓！咔嚓！机器鲨鱼冲向罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西飞快地躲开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲨鱼张大的大嘴差点儿咬到她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地面街道上的人们用手指着天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会飞的机器鲨鱼！”一个男人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“逃命啊！”一个女人大声喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲨鱼再次向罗西飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲨鱼的嘴巴张得大大的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！罗西对着鲨鱼吹冷气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲨鱼的下巴当场被冻住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西抓住鲨鱼，使劲儿把它扔到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它被摔成碎片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我要去抓邦尼•博恩斯了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！ 她看到海盗船飞过美罗城公园的上空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落在船的甲板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦尼•博恩斯站在船舵的旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的身边有一门大炮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你马上降落这艘船！”罗西大声喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要送你去监狱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“监狱！”鹦鹉大声唱到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”邦尼•博恩斯把大炮对准罗西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>点燃了导火线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘭！一枚炮弹发射了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳上前去抓住了炮弹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦尼•博恩斯睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么可以……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把炮弹重新扔给邦尼•博恩斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海盗跳着躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，她又点燃了导火线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的眼睛睁得大大的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛发射出桔色的光，把大炮熔化了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”邦尼想要逃走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西再次用眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦尼用钩子挡住了激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>激光弹开，击中了船舵。哐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”海盗船坠落在公园的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦尼紧紧抓住栏杆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船舱裂开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海盗们从银行里抢来的钱都掉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克大吃一惊。“海盗的宝藏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉指着甲板说。“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西站在邦尼前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海盗回头一看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正站在船的木板上，离地面很高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察们都在下面等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有两个选择。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在去监狱，或者你走完木板以后再去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走木板！”鹦鹉唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦尼•博恩斯低下头，“哎！我们现在去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久，罗西在公园里找到了朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去哪儿了？” 玛拉问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你错过了所有精彩的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吗？”罗西问，“你们找到那个箱子了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看到了更好的。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“海盗的宝藏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿找到的。你大概早就知道，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”杰克说，“罗西怎么可能知道？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西发现灌木丛里有什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宝藏箱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跑过去看里面装了什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西想，“我的秘密还是安全的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>